<P>THE TUTOR OF TRUTH. BY THE AUTHOR OF THE PUPIL OF PLEASURE, &amp;c. &amp;c. IN TWO VOLUMES.</P>
<P>VOL. I.</P>
<P>However Hypocri&s;y may flouri&s;h for a time, even its happie&s;t moments are clouded, and TRUTH &s;hall at la&s;t prevail.</P>
<P>LONDON, Printed for RICHARDSON and URQUHART, under the <HI>Royal Exchange.</HI></P>
<P>M DCC LXXIX.</P>
</DIV1>
