<PB REF="2" MS="y">
<PB REF="3">
<P>TO LADY MILLER, OF BATH-EASTON VILLA, THESE VOLUMES ARE INSCRIBED By her mo&s;t obedient, and Obliged humble Servant,</P>
<CLOSER><SIGNED>THE AUTHOR.</SIGNED></CLOSER>
